# Runtime caches/exports go under data/cache/ or data/exports/, both
# excluded. Source-of-truth files (e.g. data/watchlist.yaml) stay tracked.
data/cache/
data/exports/

# Session-scratch directory (Phase 2c, ADR 024 repo-hygiene rule).
# Holds ephemeral working files: session-handoff prompts for fresh
# Claude Code sessions, design proposals pending advisor review,
# anything that isn't a permanent architectural record. Architectural
# memory lives in docs/adr/, docs/*.md, ADR catalogs in
# PROJECT_OVERVIEW.md, TODO.md, README.md — those stay committed.
# notes/ does not.
notes/
